pi-extension/test/.pi/

# Per-cwd remote-pi runtime config (agent_name, auto_start_relay) — machine-local
# state written by `remote-pi claude` / the wizard, never repo content. Matches
# any `.pi/` dir at any depth (root, pi-extension/, subprojects).
.pi/
